ults.htm HK Sevens]</small>\n\n===Pool E===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!width=175 |Team\n!width=25 abbr=\"Played\" |Pld\n!width=25 abbr=\"Won\" |W\n!width=25 abbr=\"Drawn\" |D\n!width=25 abbr=\"Lost\" |L\n!width=32 abbr=\"Points for\" |PF\n!width=32 abbr=\"Points against\" |PA\n!width=32 abbr=\"Points difference\" |PD\n!width=25 abbr=\"Points\" |Pts\n|- bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{ru7|FIJ}}\n|3||3||0||0||138||0||138||9\n|-bgcolor=\"#ccffcc\"\n|align=left|{{ru7|WAL}}\n|3||2||0||1||85||24||61||7\n|-bgcolor=\"#ffddbb\"\n|align=left|{{ru7|CHN}}\n|3||1||0||2||34||129|| \u201395||5\n|- bgcolor=\"#ffddbb\"\n|align=left|{{ru7|SIN}}\n|3||0||0||3||14||118|| \u2013104||3\n|}\n<small>Source: [http://web.archive.org/web/20020623180939/http://www.hksevens.com.hk/results.htm HK Sevens]</small>\n\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 22 March \n|time    = 18:28\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|FIJ}}\n|score   = 55\u20130\n|away    = {{ru7|SIN}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 22 March\n|time    = 20:40\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|WAL}}\n|score   = 56\u20130\n|away    = {{ru7|CHN}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 23 March\n|time    = 12:14\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|WAL}}\n|score   = 29\u20137\n|away    = {{ru7|SIN}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 23 March\n|time    = 14:26\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|FIJ}} \n|score   = 66\u20130\n|away    = {{ru7|CHN}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 23 March\n|time    = 16:38\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|CHN}} \n|score   = 34\u20137\n|away    = {{ru7|SIN}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n----\n{{rugbybox\n|date    = 23 March\n|time    = 18:50\n|home    = {{ru7-rt|FIJ}} \n|score   = 17\u20130\n|away    = {{ru7|WAL}}\n|stadium = [[Hong Kong Stadium]], Hong Kong\n}}\n<small>Source: [http://web.archive.org/web/20020623180939/http://www.hksevens.com.hk/results.htm 